<div class="post-date">Apr 10</div>
<h2><a https://yarnetsky.github.io/ontheriversedge/901.html" title="Blooming on the river"> Blooming on the river</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>The Japanese companies in our city donate a number of blossoming cherry trees that are on our riverfront. They are beautiful right now, every branch is enveloped with blooms. Darlene took this photo yesterday.</p>

	<p><img alt="bridgesmall.jpg" src="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/archives/bridgesmall.jpg" width="346" height="424" border="0" /></p>

